      "rationale": "Validation performed on the identical non-cannulated 7.5 mm production device under the identical ASTM F1717 static compression-bending protocol specified in the COU. Two-laboratory design provides inter-laboratory reproducibility evidence. Validation scenario is maximally relevant to the COU."
    }
