    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieves level 2 against a required level 3; this gap is accepted based on regulatory precedent and the availability of clinical and fatigue data in the broader submission package. All three QoIs satisfy pre-registered acceptance bounds. The assessment team concludes that the FEA modeling framework has sufficient credibility for the stated COU.",
